{"tid":1546320,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)跳閘成功感get!!!!!囡囡用仰慕眼神望住我！","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T15:45:58.000Z","uid":243527,"like":55,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"243a32587e12dcc0eb31a41fbf4cbb6f54aba744","tid":1546320,"uid":243527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:45:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n啱啱放學<br />\n見冇人跳就自己跳自high下啦<br />\n咁入閘嘅時候冇乜特別就唔講啦<br />\n但係一出閘嘅時候<br />\n我一個C朗轉身<br />\n見到後面有個黃衫<br />\n咁就本來諗住跑啦<br />\n點知睇真啲<br />\n屌！原來係條索女<br />\n佢手執員工證<br />\n我再望上少少<br />\n佢用仰慕嘅眼神望住我<br />\n有冇咁撚索啊！<br />\n我同佢擦身而過<br />\n但好後悔點解冇企喺度<br />\n你搜我身啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rnRG0hC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrnRG0hC.png&h=d05eb1b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db26ec5b7b6d00a9c06884cd31bc6783f42f28e0","tid":1546320,"uid":243527,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:45:53.000Z","msg":"好想溝佢"},{"pid":"d73cb21b7f6ca830fbf8104822349aa00713ed21","tid":1546320,"uid":243527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"有啲後悔點解唔入返去"},{"pid":"4c7976d0552fddce9e18c2903e4f3198cc60013d","tid":1546320,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bb3a454ec26f66e2134f4e6ea9ce0ef27faf92e","tid":1546320,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.c